channel.title: Prime - Hern [Ambient/Drone/Noise]
channel.description:
This is one of my first non-sample based songs in quite some time on this account and I'm pretty proud of it. This probably isn't going to be part of a bigger project, though I may do something similar to this in the future as I've enjoyed it quite a bit.
Link is here: https://soundcloud.com/hernmusicofficial/prime
Hope you guys enjoy. If you have any constructive criticism, please feel free to reply with it.
